atch your current workflow before committing."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#2563eb]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#2563eb]","children":4}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Vendor payment automation",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"Some platforms (Vic.ai, Docyt) execute payments. Others (Dext) stop at data extraction. Decide whether you want an end-to-end platform or a best-of-breed capture tool."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"className":"flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111] p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#2563eb]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#2563eb]","children":5}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-white","children":["Compliance and audit trail",":"]}]," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-white/70","children":"For public companies or complex audits, verify the platform's audit trail quality. You need complete documentation of who approved what and when."}]]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"Frequently Asked Questions"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","details","0",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#2563eb]","children":["What is the typical ROI of AP automation?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Manual invoice processing costs $12-15 per invoice (IOFM benchmark). AI automation reduces this to $2-4. For a company processing 500 invoices/month, that's $48,000-$78,000 in annual savings against a typical $15,000-$30,000 annual software cost. Most companies see payback within 3-6 months."}]]}],["$","details","1",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#2563eb]","children":["How does AI AP automation handle complex multi-line invoices?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Modern systems like Vic.ai handle multi-line invoices with different GL coding per line. The AI learns to split coding based on invoice type, vendor, and line-item descriptions. Complex invoices with 20+ lines are handled well by deep learning systems; simpler OCR tools may struggle."}]]}],["$","details","2",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#2563eb]","children":["What's the difference between OCR-based and AI-based AP tools?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"OCR (optical character recognition) extracts text from documents — it identifies numbers and words. AI goes further: it understands context, applies GL coding based on learned patterns, routes approvals based on rules, and detects anomalies. Pure OCR tools require extensive manual rule-setting; AI tools learn and adapt."}]]}],["$","details","3",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#2563eb]","children":["Can AP automation handle PO matching (3-way match)?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Enterprise platforms like Vic.ai support 2-way (invoice to PO) and 3-way (invoice to PO to receipt) matching. Mid-market tools vary — verify with vendors. Three-way matching is complex and typically requires PO data from your ERP to be accessible to the AP automation tool."}]]}],["$","details","4",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#2563eb]","children":["How do we handle vendor onboarding and banking information securely?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"All enterprise AP platforms have secure vendor onboarding workflows with bank account verification. This is a critical security area — AP fraud via vendor impersonation is a major attack vector. Verify the platform has: email domain verification, callback confirmation for bank changes, and multi-person approval for new vendor banking details."}]]}],["$","details","5",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#2563eb]","children":["How long does AP automation implementation take?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-white/40 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180","fill":"none","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","stroke":"currentColor","children":["$","path",null,{"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","strokeWidth":2,"d":"M19 9l-7 7-7-7"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/10 px-5 pb-5 pt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70","children":"Dext: 1-3 days. Docyt: 1-2 weeks. Vic.ai: 4-12 weeks (full enterprise implementation with ERP integration and training). The learning curve for AI systems to reach high accuracy is typically 30-60 days regardless of platform."}]]}],["$","details","6",{"className":"group rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#111]","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-medium text-white hover:text-[#2563eb]","children":["What happens to invoices the AI can't process confidently?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-whi